OL,3,CUK to be 'hotter than Honolulu' with
OL,4,C27C sun - before Bank Holiday rain
OL,6,FParts of the UK will be hotter than
OL,7,FHawaii on Friday as temperatures hit
OL,8,F27C ahead of the Bank Holiday weekend.
OL,10,FThe East and South East of England
OL,11,Fwill see the most sun and are expected
OL,12,Fto be around 10C hotter than average
OL,13,Ftemperatures for this time of year,
OL,14,Faccording to the Met Office.
OL,16,FCardiff could also be warmer than
OL,17,FAthens, with forecasters predicting a
OL,18,Fhigh of 19C on Friday, compared to 14C
OL,19,Fexpected in Greece.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
