OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777651868
OL,3,CUK to be 'hotter than Honolulu' with
OL,4,C27C sun - before Bank Holiday rain
OL,6,FMeanwhile highs of 26C are forecast
OL,7,Ffor Honolulu, the capital of Hawaii.
OL,9,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FThe incoming hot spell is caused by
OL,15,F"very warm, humid air" coming up from
OL,16,Fthe south, Met Office meteorologist
OL,17,FSimon Partridge said.
OL,19,FIf temperatures hit 27C it would make
OL,20,FFriday the warmest day of 2026 so far.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
