FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777651868
OL,3,CUK to be 'hotter than Honolulu' with
OL,4,C27C sun - before Bank Holiday rain
OL,6,FThe record to beat is 26.6C, which was
OL,7,Frecorded at Kew Gardens, in southwest
OL,8,FLondon, on April 8.
OL,10,FHowever, not everywhere will see
OL,11,Fsunshine, as clouds will cover central
OL,12,Fparts of the UK, from Scotland, the
OL,13,FPennines and into the Midlands, which
OL,14,Fcould produce some heavy rain on
OL,15,FFriday.
OL,17,FWeather over the May Day weekend will
OL,18,Falso be changeable across the country,
OL,19,Fwith some bright spells on Saturday,
OL,20,Fbut showers expected across northern
OL,21,Fand western parts of the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
