OL,3,CUK to be 'hotter than Honolulu' with
OL,4,C27C sun - before Bank Holiday rain
OL,6,F"By the time we get to Monday, we're
OL,7,Factually going to see temperatures
OL,8,Froughly where they should be for this
OL,9,Ftime of year," Partridge said.
OL,11,F"We're looking at elevens and twelves
OL,12,F(degrees Celsius) in the north and
OL,13,Ffifteens and sixteens in the south, so
OL,14,Fit will feel quite fresh and chilly
OL,15,Fcompared to what we've had."
